text: Brilliant sharing by Dave and Justin on their extensive tea knowledge. Totally enjoyed the session on green teas.

Honest business that is dedicated to their craft and customers. They have expanded steadily over the years to include more beverage types (and cakes) while maintaining the quality of the existing goods.

Had an amazing time with Dave on the foundational roasting course! The lesson was delivered in a casual manner to facilitate discussions into many different areas! We even had a chance to roast and taste our roast in a cupping session at the end!
